WEBVTT

00:00:19.250 --> 00:00:24.359
♪The whole world is lit up♪

00:00:24.360 --> 00:00:25.979
♪Because you exist♪

00:00:25.980 --> 00:00:28.019
♪You're always♪

00:00:28.020 --> 00:00:32.679
♪Somewhere close, flying with me♪

00:00:32.680 --> 00:00:35.299
♪Go to where the wind blows♪

00:00:35.300 --> 00:00:37.019
♪Hold tight♪

00:00:37.020 --> 00:00:42.879
♪To the ray of light that belongs to us♪

00:00:42.880 --> 00:00:48.120
=Wild & Fiery=
=Episode 8=

00:00:53.820 --> 00:00:55.010
Shen Jibai,

00:00:55.540 --> 00:00:56.500
let's work together.

00:01:16.540 --> 00:01:17.980
Why are you so close to me?

00:01:21.330 --> 00:01:23.099
When discussing
such important matters, Miss Mu,

00:01:23.100 --> 00:01:24.769
aren't you on high alert?

00:01:24.770 --> 00:01:26.370
Be careful that the walls have ears.

00:01:29.970 --> 00:01:31.340
Work with me.

00:01:36.210 --> 00:01:37.290
Work with you?

00:01:37.940 --> 00:01:39.570
What's in it for me?

00:01:40.820 --> 00:01:42.379
Didn't Xu Mingzhu promise you

00:01:42.380 --> 00:01:43.780
a sum of money once it's done?

00:01:44.100 --> 00:01:45.170
I'll give you double.

00:01:45.820 --> 00:01:46.650
Of course,

00:01:47.180 --> 00:01:48.810
you can choose not to cooperate.

00:01:49.100 --> 00:01:50.140
However,

00:01:50.460 --> 00:01:53.260
if Xu Mingzhu
accidentally finds out something...

00:01:53.660 --> 00:01:55.650
The boss of Security Group,

00:01:55.970 --> 00:01:57.930
let's talk, shall we?

00:01:57.940 --> 00:01:59.260
I came to the Mu family

00:01:59.300 --> 00:02:01.060
because of a transfer record.

00:02:01.250 --> 00:02:02.730
You're looking for Mu Chenzhou.

00:02:18.140 --> 00:02:19.530
Are you threatening me?

00:02:20.420 --> 00:02:21.500
Yes.

00:02:37.020 --> 00:02:38.620
(What exactly is the connection)

00:02:39.050 --> 00:02:40.740
(between these two pendants?)

00:02:45.930 --> 00:02:47.690
It's not impossible to work with you,

00:02:47.860 --> 00:02:49.259
but from now on,

00:02:49.260 --> 00:02:50.089
information

00:02:50.090 --> 00:02:51.019
must be shared.

00:02:51.020 --> 00:02:52.209
Your news

00:02:52.210 --> 00:02:53.929
must also be shared with me immediately.

00:02:53.930 --> 00:02:55.340
In dangerous situations,

00:02:55.650 --> 00:02:57.300
you must follow my arrangements.

00:02:57.580 --> 00:02:59.220
You absolutely cannot act like today.

00:02:59.460 --> 00:03:00.410
Deal.

00:03:17.860 --> 00:03:18.529
(Boss,)

00:03:18.530 --> 00:03:20.180
(take a look at this post.)

00:03:20.650 --> 00:03:22.809
(Mu Zhiyu,
Business Director of Mu Group,)

00:03:22.810 --> 00:03:24.369
(used her position)

00:03:24.370 --> 00:03:25.920
(to first use the auction's name)

00:03:25.920 --> 00:03:28.400
(to trick her stepmom into buying
Hong's "Classic of Mountains and Seas".)

00:03:28.420 --> 00:03:30.690
(Then, she feigned
an intent to donate the painting,)

00:03:30.900 --> 00:03:32.979
(only to find someone
to damage the artwork.)

00:03:32.980 --> 00:03:35.699
(In reality, she hid the painting away)

00:03:35.700 --> 00:03:37.810
(to achieve both fame and fortune.)

00:03:40.860 --> 00:03:41.419
Exposing

00:03:41.420 --> 00:03:42.739
the heiress of Mu Group's

00:03:42.740 --> 00:03:44.500
hidden secrets.

00:03:44.900 --> 00:03:46.130
You're trending.

00:03:55.370 --> 00:03:57.259
This post is an anonymous tip.

00:03:57.260 --> 00:03:58.299
The poster claims

00:03:58.300 --> 00:04:01.130
the news came from an insider.

00:04:01.210 --> 00:04:03.579
The public outcry online
is fermenting quickly.

00:04:03.580 --> 00:04:07.060
Discussions and shares
on social media are still rising.

00:04:09.980 --> 00:04:11.930
Fine. You may leave.

00:04:16.530 --> 00:04:17.580
Mu Zhiyu.

00:04:20.210 --> 00:04:22.019
Is this how you
"discuss cooperation" with Hong

00:04:22.020 --> 00:04:23.140
as you mentioned before?

00:04:23.330 --> 00:04:25.289
Do you know
what they're saying out there?

00:04:25.290 --> 00:04:27.769
Do you see how much
Mu Group's stock price has dropped?

00:04:27.770 --> 00:04:29.880
(Hong Art Studio)

00:04:32.620 --> 00:04:33.700
This is impossible.

00:04:34.140 --> 00:04:35.969
I just went to Hong's studio.

00:04:35.970 --> 00:04:37.579
How could they send a lawyer's letter

00:04:37.580 --> 00:04:38.969
without any prior word?

00:04:38.970 --> 00:04:40.140
You went there,

00:04:40.410 --> 00:04:41.610
but did you see anyone?

00:04:41.670 --> 00:04:43.900
You didn't even see them,
so what are you still defending?

00:04:45.620 --> 00:04:46.969
(Shen Jibai,)

00:04:46.970 --> 00:04:48.780
(was it you who tipped them off?)

00:04:49.060 --> 00:04:50.050
Don't worry.

00:04:50.500 --> 00:04:52.169
I will handle the matter with Hong.

00:04:52.170 --> 00:04:54.499
I'll definitely give
Mu Group a satisfactory explanation.

00:04:54.500 --> 00:04:55.530
Fine.

00:04:55.730 --> 00:04:57.490
Then, I'll be waiting
for that explanation.

00:04:57.650 --> 00:04:58.939
If you can't handle it,

00:04:58.940 --> 00:05:01.090
leave Mu Group as soon as possible.

00:05:05.770 --> 00:05:06.259
Captain Shen,

00:05:06.260 --> 00:05:08.900
you're doing a great job
as a double agent.

00:05:10.140 --> 00:05:12.380
You told Xu Mingzhu the news so quickly.

00:05:13.090 --> 00:05:14.580
Since I'm a spy,

00:05:14.770 --> 00:05:16.460
I have to give
my employer some benefits.

00:05:20.770 --> 00:05:23.499
Miss Yan was clearly
already discussing cooperation.

00:05:23.500 --> 00:05:25.459
How could they send a lawyer's letter

00:05:25.460 --> 00:05:26.850
right after that post went up?

00:05:28.730 --> 00:05:30.290
Don't you find it strange?

00:05:33.060 --> 00:05:34.379
It is indeed very strange.

00:05:34.380 --> 00:05:35.819
(Lawyer's Letter)

00:05:35.820 --> 00:05:36.699
But this letter

00:05:36.700 --> 00:05:39.020
was indeed sent
to the company's legal department.

00:05:40.770 --> 00:05:42.380
Is there something
wrong with the letter?

00:05:46.500 --> 00:05:47.459
This won't do.

00:05:47.460 --> 00:05:48.940
I have to go see Miss Yan.

00:05:56.330 --> 00:05:57.340
Miss Mu,

00:05:57.380 --> 00:05:58.379
concerning this matter,

00:05:58.380 --> 00:06:00.490
thank you for contacting our studio.

00:06:00.730 --> 00:06:03.019
We have compared
the lawyer's letter you faxed

00:06:03.020 --> 00:06:04.819
with Mr. Hong's private seal

00:06:04.820 --> 00:06:05.729
at the studio.

00:06:05.730 --> 00:06:08.169
We confirmed that the seal
on the letter is a forgery.

00:06:08.170 --> 00:06:08.969
That's great.

00:06:08.970 --> 00:06:10.169
Thank you, Miss Yan.

00:06:10.170 --> 00:06:11.089
You're welcome.

00:06:11.090 --> 00:06:12.209
Business is business.

00:06:12.210 --> 00:06:14.769
Our studio will never allow anyone
to commit such a heinous act

00:06:14.770 --> 00:06:16.220
as forging a private seal.

00:06:18.210 --> 00:06:19.140
By the way,

00:06:19.330 --> 00:06:20.410
I wonder

00:06:20.460 --> 00:06:22.260
if Mr. Hong has returned
from his vacation.

00:06:22.770 --> 00:06:24.460
Regarding our cooperation,

00:06:24.820 --> 00:06:26.530
I'd like to try to win him over again.

00:06:27.210 --> 00:06:28.259
I'm confident

00:06:28.260 --> 00:06:29.940
that as long as this matter is resolved,

00:06:30.060 --> 00:06:30.819
we

00:06:30.820 --> 00:06:33.610
can smoothly proceed with everything
related to the exclusive auction.

00:06:38.330 --> 00:06:39.379
Miss Mu,

00:06:39.380 --> 00:06:40.969
Mr. Hong has returned.

00:06:40.970 --> 00:06:42.340
He can see you now.

00:06:53.650 --> 00:06:54.649
Mr. Hong,

00:06:54.650 --> 00:06:55.900
Miss Mu is here.

00:06:58.090 --> 00:06:59.730
You are Mr. Hong?

00:07:00.380 --> 00:07:01.209
Miss Mu,

00:07:01.210 --> 00:07:02.140
nice to meet you.

00:07:07.170 --> 00:07:08.819
I'm sorry, Miss Mu.

00:07:08.820 --> 00:07:10.699
Because Mr. Hong
just returned from abroad,

00:07:10.700 --> 00:07:12.139
he hasn't been feeling well.

00:07:12.140 --> 00:07:13.899
That's why his voice
sounds a bit strange.

00:07:13.900 --> 00:07:15.050
Please bear with us.

00:07:15.090 --> 00:07:16.090
Of course.

00:07:16.410 --> 00:07:20.020
I'm already very surprised that Mr. Hong
could make an appearance today.

00:07:20.620 --> 00:07:21.850
Regarding

00:07:21.900 --> 00:07:23.379
the damage to your painting,

00:07:23.380 --> 00:07:24.970
I am truly sorry, Mr. Hong.

00:07:25.090 --> 00:07:25.899
Today,

00:07:25.900 --> 00:07:27.700
I'm also representing Mu Group...

00:07:29.650 --> 00:07:32.970
This is a seal forgery appraisal
signed by me.

00:07:33.460 --> 00:07:34.169
It can prove

00:07:34.170 --> 00:07:36.089
that the seal
on the lawyer's letter you received

00:07:36.090 --> 00:07:37.260
is a forgery.

00:07:38.200 --> 00:07:41.449
♪Returning from the ashes
to craft the plan♪

00:07:41.450 --> 00:07:44.009
♪From now on, no one can break it♪

00:07:44.010 --> 00:07:46.120
(Certification
of Official Seal Authenticity)

00:07:46.370 --> 00:07:48.570
♪Love has vanished♪

00:07:48.580 --> 00:07:50.410
I'm truly grateful to you, Mr. Hong.

00:07:51.020 --> 00:07:52.259
Since

00:07:52.260 --> 00:07:54.410
the matter
of the lawyer's letter is resolved,

00:07:54.700 --> 00:07:57.340
I wonder if we could
discuss cooperation again?

00:07:57.530 --> 00:07:59.940
I think you have
misunderstood something, Miss Mu.

00:08:00.900 --> 00:08:02.379
The forgery of a private seal

00:08:02.380 --> 00:08:05.170
concerns the reputation
of the studio and me.

00:08:05.580 --> 00:08:07.580
Helping you was only natural.

00:08:09.620 --> 00:08:11.380
As for cooperation,

00:08:11.500 --> 00:08:12.939
what makes you think

00:08:12.940 --> 00:08:15.900
I'd work with someone
who destroyed my painting?

00:08:17.470 --> 00:08:20.849
♪Waking up between our dreams♪

00:08:20.850 --> 00:08:22.380
If I weren't sincere,

00:08:22.700 --> 00:08:24.650
I wouldn't have come
to discuss this with you.

00:08:26.820 --> 00:08:27.849
Look.

00:08:27.850 --> 00:08:30.289
This is
the "Classic of Mountains and Seas"

00:08:30.290 --> 00:08:31.850
repaired by a restoration master.

00:08:32.500 --> 00:08:34.289
Though there's no way

00:08:34.290 --> 00:08:36.220
to fully restore it
to its original state,

00:08:36.570 --> 00:08:39.540
the painting itself has been restored
to the greatest extent possible.

00:08:40.290 --> 00:08:41.490
Please, have a look.

00:08:41.640 --> 00:08:43.689
♪If destined souls must part♪

00:08:43.690 --> 00:08:45.619
♪The broken mirror shall mend again♪

00:08:45.620 --> 00:08:46.899
♪In this life, one life is given♪

00:08:46.900 --> 00:08:50.419
♪In exchange for a lifelong bond♪

00:08:50.420 --> 00:08:55.130
♪And a promise of safety for a lifetime♪

00:09:00.900 --> 00:09:02.099
I'll take the painting.

00:09:02.100 --> 00:09:04.180
I appreciate the gesture, Miss Mu.

00:09:05.220 --> 00:09:07.250
Since that's the case,

00:09:07.650 --> 00:09:08.929
about the cooperation...

00:09:08.930 --> 00:09:10.339
About the cooperation,

00:09:10.340 --> 00:09:12.060
let's discuss it another day.

00:09:12.170 --> 00:09:14.090
If you have nothing else, Miss Mu,

00:09:14.620 --> 00:09:15.770
then please.

00:09:18.570 --> 00:09:19.730
Miss Yan.

00:09:22.530 --> 00:09:24.540
This is my auction proposal.

00:09:24.860 --> 00:09:27.660
I hope Mr. Hong
will look it over before deciding.

00:09:32.260 --> 00:09:33.370
Miss Mu.

00:09:51.370 --> 00:09:55.600
♪Light comes beaming in♪

00:09:55.740 --> 00:10:00.109
♪Landing on my skin♪

00:10:00.110 --> 00:10:04.600
♪Warms the space you left behind♪

00:10:08.820 --> 00:10:13.080
♪Shadows move around♪

00:10:13.170 --> 00:10:17.369
♪Awake, racing thoughts♪

00:10:17.370 --> 00:10:21.900
♪Try to keep the memories safe♪

00:10:25.500 --> 00:10:31.290
♪Don't slip away♪

00:10:33.740 --> 00:10:38.309
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:10:38.310 --> 00:10:42.709
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:10:42.710 --> 00:10:47.030
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:10:47.050 --> 00:10:51.030
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:10:51.500 --> 00:10:55.809
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:10:55.810 --> 00:11:00.139
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:11:00.140 --> 00:11:04.449
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:11:04.450 --> 00:11:10.600
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪